Onome Akinbode-James (ka amụrụ na Machị 9, 2000) bụ onye egwuregwu basketball nke Naijiria
Ọ nọchitere anya Naịjirịa na FIBA Africa Under-16 Championship for Women
Ọ na-egwu basketball kọleji maka otu egwuregwu basketball ụmụ nwanyị Duke Blue Devils
Onome bụ (amụrụ na Machị 9, 2000) na Abeokuta, Ogun steeti , South western Nigeria
Ọ gụrụ akwụkwọ praịmarị na Abeokuta

Ọ nọ n'ụlọakwụkwọ sekọndrị ya na Naịjirịa mgbe ọ malitere ịgba bọọlụ basketball mgbe ọ dị afọ iri na anọ. Ọ gafere na Blair Academy na Blairstown Township, New Jersey, ebe ọ gụsịrị akwụkwọ sekọndrị ya.
A kpọbatara Onome na Blair Academy mgbe FIBA Africa Under-16 Championship for Women gasịrị
N'afọ ya nke okenye, ọ nwetara akara 13.0, 11.8 rebounds, na 2.2 blocks kwa egwuregwu.
Onome nyere TED Talk na ụlọakwụkwọ sekọndrị ya Blair Academy n'oge ọ nọ n'ụlọ akwụkwọ sekọndrị
A kpọrọ okwu a Africa, Country or Continent: The Broken Perception
Onye bụbu onye isi nchịkwa Duke bụ Joanne P
McCallie kpọbatara Onome na Duke Blue Devils
N'oge ọhụrụ ya, ọ nwetara akara anọ na 5.7 rebounds kwa egwuregwu.

Onome nọchitere anya Naịjirịa na FIBA Africa Under-16 Championship for Women ebe ọ nwetara akara 5.7, 10.3 rebounds na 0.8 na-enyere aka kwa egwuregwu n'oge asọmpi ahụ.
Ndị otu Naịjirịa ritere ihe nrite ọla ọcha mgbe ha meriri obodo Mali 57–46 na Final, si otú a mee ka ha ruo eru na World U-17 Championship for Women
